Title: Metadisourse Markers
Author: Sicheng Wang
Date: 2024-03-16
Description: It counted the numbers of each metadiscourse markers categorized by Sicheng Wang according to Hyland and Tse(2004). The selected source text is `Control of the activity of CAR-T cells within tumours via focused ultrasound` following with its translation translated by Sicheng Wang


Environment:
  - Operating System: Windows 11
  - R Version: R version 4.3.2 (2023-10-31)
  - RStudio Version: 2023.12.0.369

Dependencies:
  - knitr: 1.45
  - stringr: 1.5.1
  - readr: 2.1.5
  - readtext: 0.91
  - fs: 1.6.3

References:
Hyland, K., & Tse, P. (2004). Metadiscourse in academic writing: A reappraisal. Applied linguistics, 25(2), 156-177.